description: Demolition of existing residential buildings on site  and construction of buildings between three and nine storeys to provide 117 residential units, 300 sqm of commercial floorspace comprising retail, restaurant, business and non-residential institution (Use Classes A1, A3, B1 and D2). Provision of  open space improvements and car parking.
